content.p: Check out the latest dates on our calendar - join us to try something new, challenge yourself or support our Green and Gold teams! Try out our fitness suite for free and our friendly team will be on hand to show you round and chat about our staff, alumni, associate and public memberships. Find out more about how to manage career development and searching for jobs alongside your sporting activities with this workshop led by the University's Careers team. Our Prospect Days are the perfect opportunity to immerse yourself in the #GreenandGold and discover all that's on offer with our performance programmes. Found out more about how to develop your leadership style via sport with this workshop led by the University's Careers team. Join the University of Nottingham team to take on the virtual Catcher Car in this unique event, with 100% of all entry fees going to spinal cord research. Find out more about some of our most popular annual event series here at University of Nottingham Sport including the latest dates, past results and live streams. +44 (0)115 748 7000 sport@nottingham.ac.uk Find our opening times here.
